     eexxppaanndd, uunneexxppaanndd - expand tabs to spaces, and vice versa

SSYYNNOOPPSSIISS
     eexxppaanndd [--_t_a_b_s_t_o_p] [--_t_a_b_1,_t_a_b_2,...,_t_a_b_n] [_f_i_l_e ...]
